<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[أَوْن]</span> الأَوْنان: العِدْلان. واحدهما أَوْن.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">والأوْن:</span> الخُرْج.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[هـ‍]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[أَوْهِ]</span>: كلمة تَحَزُّن، قال <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَأَوْهِ مِنَ الذِّكْرَى إِذَا ما ذَكَرْتُها ... ومِنْ بُعْدِ أَرْضٍ بَيْنَنَا وسَمَاءِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فُعْل]</span>، بضم الفاء<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
